The '''Kanchen Sector Conference''' was an annual conference of the [[Kanchen sector/Legends|Kanchen sector's]] leaders held on [[Pakrik Major]]. It was led by the [[Grandiose Elector]] of Pakrik Major. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] attended the conference as [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] representatives in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]]. The 19 ABY meeting lasted for at least fifteen days.

